	Alternative{lang='vri', text='sahassilokadhātuṃ'}
	Alternative{lang='pī.', text='sahassīlokadhātuṃ'}}
sarena viññāpesī’ti. Bhagavā pana, bhante, arahaṃ sammāsambuddho kīvatakaṃ pahoti sarena viññāpetu’’nti? ‘‘Sāvako so, ānanda, appameyyā tathāgatā’’ti.

